        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[Major CIROH Hub update for February!]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="theme-admonition theme-admonition-info admonition_xJq3 alert alert--info"><div class="admonitionHeading_Gvgb"><span class="admonitionIcon_Rf37"><svg viewBox="0 0 14 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7 2.3c3.14 0 5.7 2.56 5.7 5.7s-2.56 5.7-5.7 5.7A5.71 5.71 0 0 1 1.3 8c0-3.14 2.56-5.7 5.7-5.7zM7 1C3.14 1 0 4.14 0 8s3.14 7 7 7 7-3.14 7-7-3.14-7-7-7zm1 3H6v5h2V4zm0 6H6v2h2v-2z"></path></svg></span>info</div><div class="admonitionContent_BuS1"><p>This update marked the first major release of CIROH Hub. All change notes are relative to CIROH DocuHub's release from February 2nd, 2026.</p></div></div>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="migrated-content">Migrated content<a href="http://ciroh.org/staging/main/release-notes/v20260218#migrated-content" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Migrated content" title="Direct link to Migrated content" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>The following pages were migrated from CIROH Portal:</p>
<ul>
<li class=""><a class="" href="http://ciroh.org/staging/main/apps">Apps</a></li>
<li class=""><a class="" href="http://ciroh.org/staging/main/datasets">Datasets</a></li>
<li class=""><a class="" href="http://ciroh.org/staging/main/courses">Courses</a></li>
<li class=""><a class="" href="http://ciroh.org/staging/main/presentations">Presentations</a></li>
<li class=""><a class="" href="http://ciroh.org/staging/main/publications">Publications</a></li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="new-content">New content<a href="http://ciroh.org/staging/main/release-notes/v20260218#new-content" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to New content" title="Direct link to New content" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li class=""><a class="" href="http://ciroh.org/staging/main/notebooks">Notebooks</a>: Explore JupyterHub notebooks hosted via HydroShare</li>
<li class=""><a class="" href="http://ciroh.org/staging/main/working-groups">Working Groups</a>: Discover venues for collaboration</li>
<li class=""><a class="" href="http://ciroh.org/staging/main/contribute">Contribute</a>: Revamped to reflect the merger of DocuHub and Portal</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="blog-posts-and-news-updates">Blog posts and news updates<a href="http://ciroh.org/staging/main/release-notes/v20260218#blog-posts-and-news-updates" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Blog posts and news updates" title="Direct link to Blog posts and news updates" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li class="">New blog post: "<a class="" href="http://ciroh.org/staging/main/blog/awi-psu-collab2">Hourly Differentiable Modeling Arrives in the NGIAB-NRDS NextGen Ecosystem</a>"</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="updates">Updates<a href="http://ciroh.org/staging/main/release-notes/v20260218#updates" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Updates" title="Direct link to Updates" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li class="">Updated aesthetics site-wide</li>
</ul>]]></content>
